Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fastest way to get others to understand you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is to close the distance between yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, honorific suffixes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By adding "-kun" or "-san" to a person's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you project an air of being polite, but\N reserved, and the gap does not shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the courage to simply call them by their name,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even come up with a nickname or pet name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing so, you become special to\N them and a lasting friendship will form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sai's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at an art book?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're reading!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even Sai acts normal sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto and I are going to visit Kakashi-sensei. You wanna come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a member of team Kakashi now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My revenge is everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I can exact it, I don't care what happens to me or anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If sacrificing my body to Orochimaru is the only way to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd give up my life a million times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is the source of your hidden powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never would've thought you'd have something like this inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I dreaming about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah man... Sai's coming, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bumped into him at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I planned this out so it'd just be the two of us, like a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! If you've got enough time to think up\N stuff like that, go study some ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah, studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you guys go to the library. It's so lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, you don't just need to train physically, but mentally, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a complete dunce!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah ha. Sakura-san doesn't use any honorifics with Naruto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan, that was harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naruto... S-Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I join your conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you see, I was reading about how to open up to people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it said to try dropping honorifics, or use a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing so, you can become friends faster and easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's what you're so nervous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that book you had earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to come up with nicknames for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't think of any,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought dropping the honorifics was good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Sai's taking this so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't decide on nicknames, they just kinda happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They usually have something to do with\N the person's traits or characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, take Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Naruto the Idiot" or "Naruto the Jerk" fit him perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan, you're killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traits... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai's changed so much since we first met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to stare at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I think I get it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai, you're killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan, why'd you hit me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the new team member...Sai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:08:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see they've got some scratches. Did they get in a fight already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Naruto well enough to not be surprised, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, we get along very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the fabled Hatake Kakashi we heard about in Root.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei, while we were on our mission-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato told me about everything, including Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't bring Sasuke back, not like we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you just need to become even stronger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I saw, he's gotten so strong, so fast, it was unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Tsunade-sama, she said he's\N probably learning forbidden techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And considering he's got Kabuto behind\N him, probably using special drugs as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just reading isn't going to help me understand\N people who experiment on human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll have to get strong in an\N unbelievably short amount of time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I've just been lying around doing nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been mulling over this the whole time\N I've been here. And I've finally got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the training's more suited for Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or more accurately, Naruto's the only one suited for {\i1}it{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, if this works, you may, in a sense, even surpass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me surpass you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be working with you the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll be unlike any training you've done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What'll we be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to learn the most powerful\N technique you can do by creating it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you're going to learn a technique\N more powerful than Rasengan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to do so, you'll need to invest a\N massive amount of time and effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like those stories where the main\N character gets ridiculously strong in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's also going to be different from\N Rasengan, which someone else created,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and which you learned through careful instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Massive amounts of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't {\i1}have{\i0} time! Sasuke's-!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. I figured out how we can do it in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ya doing, Kakashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma-sensei! Would you at least knock first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heggo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Naruto and Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already finished your mis-?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this have to happen today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, relax... Start with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job on your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll take my leave, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki is finally starting to get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before they target Konoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely a dangerous situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's also our chance to take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get serious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just call me Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about any suffixes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's kinda cute, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He reminds me of Sasuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Physically, yeah. But he's nothing like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about Sasuke from Tsunade-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can help you out the next time something comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now that that stupid Chuunin exam's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd make Chuunin easily this time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah well, maybe next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why're you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go on ahead to the barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Kakashi's invited to join you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, barbecue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call the seat next to Sai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi and I have a few things to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my treat, so no objections, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you gonna say? About the training?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the training?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later? But I wanna know now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, we can't start while I'm still in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he had to go home and help his dad\N collect deer antlers for making medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always right on time for meetings about missions and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She mustn't have heard my warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet, I call his share!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji! At least introduce yourself to Sai-kun first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Word is the other villages are gearing up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're after the Bijuu, they'll clearly\N target the village. Well, Naruto, at any rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to leave me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm concerned about Akatsuki's movements, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Naruto be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, they even took out Gaara. If they come after him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First impressions are extremely important to friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to come up with a nickname right away, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm Akimichi Chouji from the Akimichi\N clan. Nice to meet you. Sai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traits, characteristics...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't... {\i1}Not that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fa-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai, never ever {\i1}ever{\i0} say the word "fatty" in front of Chouji, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you gonna say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up with nicknames is hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Yamanaka Ino, from the Yamanaka Florists!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you simply use a girl's actual traits for a nickname, they get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So perhaps if I try the opposite, that won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach her a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Ino get to be gorgeous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rat, Sheep, Monkey, Rabbit, Rabbit, Bird, Ox, Ox, Monkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rat, Sheep, Dragon, Rabbit, Rabbit, Horse, Rabbit, Horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger, Ox, Bird, Boar, Boar, Rat, Rat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bird, Rabbit, Rabbit, Horse, Dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bird, Dragon, Snake, Dragon, Monkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong one, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:11.70,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,Kodomo no koro mita niji wo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:11.70,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,If I look up now for the rainbow I saw as a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:17.30,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,ima miageru to nana iro de wa naku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:17.30,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,there are no longer the seven colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:23.44,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagate kiri ga kakari
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:23.44,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,only mist and fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:30.02,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,Jikan wa sugi kawatte yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:30.02,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,As time passes by, and the world around me changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:36.66,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi wo sagashitemo doko ni mo inai
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:36.66,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter where I search for you, you're nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:42.46,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,Me wo toji, kokoro hiraite
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:42.46,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,So I close my eyes, and open my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:48.77,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,mata nagamete mitemo nanimo kawaranai no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:48.77,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to know, if I gaze up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:54.54,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,tashikamete mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:54.54,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,will things be different this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:21:01.41,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunao ni narereba kono kiri ga hareru to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:21:01.41,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if I was more honest, the fog would fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:06.92,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro ni negai sou sakenderu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:06.92,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,So I pray, screaming that wish deep within my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:13.73,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanika wo nakushiteshimatta koto de sou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:13.73,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,When you lose one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:19.23,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,te ni shita mono mo kitto arun darou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:19.23,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,you gain another, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:26.11,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,Dakedo mada bokura wa otona ni tomadoi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:26.11,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, no matter how often the adults confuse us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:33.41,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,970)}ikite yuku sube sagashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:33.41,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,970)}we'll keep looking for the right way to live our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto's new training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long it'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-senpai claimed to have a brilliant idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto's the kid even Jiraiya had trouble handling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a true test of Kakashi's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:22:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Naruto Shippuuden,\N Wind, airs Thursday 4/17 at 7:30 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:22:04.85,NextEpTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(910,529)}Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} meat, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to whomever's faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was going to call you f-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.55,0:22:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai, I just told you never to call him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked a piece for you, Sai-kun! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting like such a bimbo, Ino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah ha! You just want Sai-kun for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forehead Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's a forehead girl, Ino-Pig?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in Sai-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pig?! Why you little-!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Sakura-chan, take it easy-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, stupid Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?! Stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Ino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clam it, fatty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just husky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikudan Sensha{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:58.11,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Nikudan Sensha: Meat Bullet Tank)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up with nicknames is so hard...
